	   <tr><td colspan=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;  There is one thing called bellow kiting that can be done 12+ it involves selo run ahead of a mob and bellow reapply selo ect.... That method is a pain in the wazzo you will likly die because yo miss a note and it catches up to you. I'd limit kiting till 27. Then you can charm kite. this involves finding two mobs charm one and sic it on the other hit selo and run a bit till it breaks reapply. Works well and if you dont get caught you will have little down time only problem is it is hard to end it i suggest fear kiting or bellow kiting it for its remaining HP.<br><br>     Linan, 30 Bard of Bertoxx<br>      "Whoops was that my train?"<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
